arStrings.szText:
Using a {c_important}Werewolf{/c} Skill grants you {c_number}[SF_0 * 100|%|]{/c} increased Attack Speed for {c_number}[SF_1]{/c} seconds, stacking up to {c_number}[SF_2]{/c} times and cannot be refreshed at maximum stacks.

The damage of your {c_important}Storm{/c} Skills is increased by {c_number}[SF_3 * 100|%|]{/c} of your Bonus Attack Speed.
